<div id="interest" class="more">
<p> Data mining, financial engineering, causal analysis, machine learning, big data analysis, 
bioinformatics,  the modelling of artificial 
neural networks. 
The applications of neural networks and ICA in time series 
prediction, portfolio management, risk analysis,
gene expression data analysis, image recognition.  Previous research interest includes 
Cantonese speech recognition, constraint satisfaction problems and
image database.
</p>

